title: Maxim Franțuz
text: Maxim Franţuz (born 4 May 1986, in <a href="Chi%C8%99in%C4%83u">Chișinău</a>) is a <a href="Moldova">Moldova</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. As of September 2009, he plays for <a href="FC%20Zimbru%20Chi%C5%9Fin%C4%83u">FC Zimbru Chişinău</a>.
